{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "385c9088-fd71-4bb1-b4b3-bbdc86c8aaa5", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/385c9088-fd71-4bb1-b4b3-bbdc86c8aaa5@1.pkg/1772597492458/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597493167", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/385c9088-fd71-4bb1-b4b3-bbdc86c8aaa5@1.pkg/1772597492458/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597493167"}, "identifier": "385c9088-fd71-4bb1-b4b3-bbdc86c8aaa5", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查对 &ldquo;走向未来&rdquo; 中过程与结果关系的理解。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③④</span><span>：哲人对登山过程的珍视，启示我们走向未来时，既要关注目标，也不能忽视过程中的体验与积累，且需在二者间找到平衡，这符合 &ldquo;走向未来&rdquo; 中应理性看待人生经历、兼顾过程与结果的知识点，故</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③④</span><span>符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>：&ldquo;确定目标后不可中途调整&rdquo; 错误，未来具有不确定性，根据实际情况调整目标是灵活规划人生的体现，并非 &ldquo;不可中途调整&rdquo;；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>故本题选 C。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>有位哲人曾与友人相约攀登远方的高山，长途跋涉后因山遥路远决定折返。友人叹惋 &ldquo;徒劳无功&rdquo;，哲人却笑着说：&ldquo;沿途的溪流、野花、林间风吟，都是此行的收获啊。&rdquo; 这位哲人的感悟给我们的人生启示是（&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span>）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①走向未来，应重视过程中的体验与成长</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②确定目标后，需坚持到底不可中途调整</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③人生的收获既包括目标实现，也包括经历中的积累</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④规划未来时，要学会在目标与过程间找到平衡</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）有位哲人曾与友人相约攀登远方的高山，长途跋涉后因山遥路远决定折返。友人叹惋 “徒劳无功”，哲人却笑着说：“沿途的溪流、野花、林间风吟，都是此行的收获啊。” 这位哲人的感悟给我们的人生启示是（     ）①走向未来，应重视过程中的体验与成长②确定目标后，需坚持到底不可中途调整③人生的收获既包括目标实现，也包括经历中的积累④规划未来时，要学会在目标与过程间找到平衡", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/385c9088-fd71-4bb1-b4b3-bbdc86c8aaa5@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984729217", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②③</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②④</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p sty